    .swiper-wrapper.stages__swiper-wrapper
      .swiper-slide.stages__swiper-slide.stages__swiper-slide--first
        .stages__card.stages__card--first
          .stages__card-bg
            picture.stages__card-bg-image(data-swiper-parallax="-300")
                <source type="image/webp" media="(max-width: 767px)" srcset="assets/img/stages/1.webp">
                <source type="image/jpg" media="(max-width: 767px)" srcset="assets/img/stages/1.jpg">
                img(src="assets/img/stages/1.webp", alt="model-1")
          h3.stages__card-title(data-swiper-parallax="-200")  Подберем модели и&nbsp;материалы
          p.stages__card-description(data-swiper-parallax="-100") Поможем с выбором существующей модели или изготовим конкретно для вас. 
          p.stages__card-description(data-swiper-parallax="-100") Заменяем цвета, карманы, отделку, фурнитуру любых моделей одежды. 
          .stages__card-arrow scroll
      .swiper-slide.stages__swiper-slide.stages__swiper-slide--second
        .stages__card.stages__card--second
          .stages__card-bg
            picture.stages__card-bg-image(data-swiper-parallax="-300")
